{"id":845081559,"question_id":2377,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 6 months","timestamp":1668673484,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"0 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/845081559/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Check if Number Has Equal Digit Count and Digit Value","memory":"40.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public boolean digitCount(String num) {\n        \n        int[] arr = new int[10];\n        \n        int len = num.length();\n        for(int i=0; i<len; i++){\n            char ch = num.charAt(i);\n            arr[ch-'0']++;\n        }\n        \n        for(int i=0; i<len; i++){\n            if(arr[i]!= (num.charAt(i)-'0'))\n                return false;\n        }\n        \n        return true;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"check-if-number-has-equal-digit-count-and-digit-value","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
